data.description: Come enjoy all that the waterfront has to offer in this towering 3 bedroom/2.5 bath home complete with elevator to make lake living even easier.  Once inside you’ll feel right at home with custom cabinetry, craftsman molding, soaking tub and vaulted ceilings.  Looking for a place to gather with your family, how does a 20ft island sound? Home has too many upgrades to list, but no detail has been left undone.  Enjoy the sounds of nature from your back porch or patio as you overlook the lake and listen to the water feature.  Located next door to the quiet community park which includes a large covered pavilion, playground, restrooms, basketball and tennis courts.   Extra 1700 sq ft of storage/garage space on the ground level, with a secondary kitchen for backyard cookouts.   Seconds away from 45 and The Woodlands but feels like you are in a secluded paradise.
